Members of civil society group on Easter Sunday, paid a condolence visit to Dr Joe, wife of late Yinka Odumakin, who passed on Saturday 3rd April, 2021. The group chant solidarity songs with Yinka Odumakin’s name recognised as a hero of democracy, but emotion betray some of the activists as they couldn’t hold back their tears. Vanguard News Nigeria   All rights reserved. This material and any other digital content on this platform may not be reproduced, published, broadcast, written or distributed in full or in part, without written permission from VANGUARD NEWS.